\c 22
\s Ahabhi anoita sungano naJehoshafati; Kufa kwaAhabhi
\p
\v 1 Zvino vakagara makore matatu kusino kurwa pakati pavaSiriya navaIsraeri.
\v 2 Zvino negore rechitatu Jehoshafati mambo waJudha wakaburukira kuna mambo waIsraeri.
\p
\v 3 Ipapo mambo waIsraeri akati kuvaranda vake, Munoziva here kuti RamotiGiriyadhi nderedu? Asi isu tigere hedu tinyerere, tisingaritori kuna mambo weSiriya.
\v 4 Akati kuna Jehoshafati, Uchaenda neni kundorwa neRamotiGiriyadhi here? Jehoshafati akati kuna mambo waIsraeri, Ini ndakaita sewe, navanhu vangu savanhu vako, namabhiza angu samabhiza ako.
\v 5 Jehoshafati akati kuna mambo waIsraeri, Dombobvunza hako shoko raJehovha nhasi.
\p
\v 6 Zvino mambo waIsraeri akaunganidza vaporofita, vanenge varume vaiva namazana mana, akati kwavari, Ndiende kundorwa neRamotiGiriyadhi here, kana ndirege? Ivo vakati, Endai, nekuti Ishe uchariisa mumaoko amambo.
\p
\v 7 Asi Jehoshafati akati, Hakuchina umwe  muporofita waJehovha pano here, timubvunze?
\p
\v 8 Mambo waIsraeri akati kuna Jehoshafati, umwe  murume uchiriko, Mikaya mwanakomana waImira, watingabvunza kuda kwaJehovha naye, asi ini ndinomuvenga, nekuti haaporofiti zvakanaka pamusoro pangu, asi zvakaipa. Jehoshafati akati, Mambo ngaarege kudaro.
\p
\v 9 Zvino mambo waIsraeri akadana muranda, akati, Kurumidza undotora Mikaya mwanakomana waImira.
\p
\v 10 Zvino mambo waIsraeri naJehoshafati mambo waJudha vakange vagere umwe  neumwe   pachigaro chake choushe, vakafuka nguvo \add dzavo\add* dzoushe padare pasuwo reSamaria; vaporofita vose vakaporofita pamberi pavo.
\p
\v 11 Zedhekia mwanakomana waKenaani akazviitira nyanga dzamatare, akati, Zvanzi naJehovha, Nedzidzi muchatunga vaSiriya, kusvikira vapera.
\p
\v 12 Navamwe vaporofita vose vakaporofita saizvozvo, vakati, Endai Ramotigiteadhi, muchakunda, nekuti Jehovha uchariisa muruoko rwamambo.
\p
\v 13 Zvino nhume yakange yanodana Mikaya yakataura kwaari, ikati, Tarirai, mashoko avaporofita anobvumirana achitaura zvakanaka kuna mambo; zvino ndinokumbira kuti shoko renyu rive seshoko romumwe wavo, mutaurewo zvakanaka.
\p
\v 14 Ipapo Mikaya akati, NaJehovha mupenyu, izvo zvinorehwa naJehovha kwandiri, ndizvo zvandichataura.
\p
\v 15 Zvino wakati achisvika kuna mambo, mambo akati kwaari, Mikaya, tiende kundorwa neRamotiGiriyadhi here, kana tirege? Akapindura, akati, Endai henyu, muchakunda, nekuti Jehovha uchariisa muruoko rwamambo.
\p
\v 16 Mambo akati kwaari, Ndinofanira kukupikisa kangani kuti undiudze chokwadi yoga nezita raJehovha?
\p
\v 17 Iye akati, Ndaona vaIsraeri vose vakapararira pamakomo samakwai asina mufudzi, Jehovha akati, Ava havana tenzi, umwe  neumwe   ngaadzokere kumusha kwake norugare.
\p
\v 18 Mambo waIsraeri akati kuna Jehoshafati, Handina kukuudza here? Kuti haangaporofiti zvakanaka pamusoro pangu, asi zvakaipa?
\p
\v 19 Mikaya akati, Zvino chinzwai shoko raJehovha, Ndakaona Jehovha agere pachigaro chake choushe, nehondo dzose dzokudenga dzimire naye kurudyi rwake nokuruboshwe rwake.
\p
\v 20 Ipapo Jehovha akati, Ndianiko uchanonyengera Ahabhi, aende, anourawa paRamotiGiriyadhi? Zvino umwe  akati zvekuti, nomumwezve akati zvekuti.
\p
\v 21 Zvino mweya ukabuda, ukamira pamberi paJehovha, ukati, Ini ndichanomunyengera.
\v 22 Jehovha akati kwauri, Neiko? Iwo ukati, Ndichaenda, ndichava mweya wenhema mumiromo yavaporofita vake vose. Iye akati, Iwe ndiwe uchamunyengera, uchakundawo; enda hako, undoita saizvozvo.
\p
\v 23 Naizvozvo zvino, tarirai Jehovha wakaisa mweya wenhema mumiromo yavaporofita venyu ava vose, asi Jehovha wakataura zvakaipa pamusoro penyu.
\p
\v 24 Ipapo Zedhekia mwanakomana waKenaani akaswedera, akarova Mikaya padama rake, akati, Mweya waJehovha wakaenda nepiko uchibva kwandiri kundotaura newe?
\v 25 Mikaya akati, Uchazviona musi uyo wauchanovanda mukamuri yomukati.
\p
\v 26 Ipapo mambo waIsraeri akati, Batai Mikaya, mumuise kuna Amoni mubati weguta, nokuna Joashi mwanakomana wamambo,
\v 27 muti, Zvanzi namambo, pinzai munhu uyu mutirongo, mumupe zvokudya zvokutambudzika, nemvura yokutambudzika, kusvikira ndichidzoka norugare.
\p
\v 28 Ipapo Mikaya akati, Kana mukadzoka norugare, Jehovha haana kutaura neni. Akati, Inzwai, imwi vanhu, imwi mose.
\p
\v 29 Naizvozvo mambo waIsraeri naJehoshafati mambo waJudha vakaenda RamotiGiriyadhi.
\v 30 Zvino mambo waIsraeri akati kuna Jehoshafati, Ini ndichazvishandura, ndigondorwa; asi iwe chifuka nguvo dzangu dzoushe. Mambo waIsraeri akazvishandura, akanorwa.
\p
\v 31 Zvino mambo weSiriya wakange araira vatariri vengoro dzake, vana makumi matatu navaviri, akati, Regai kurwa navaduku kana navakuru, asi namambo waIsraeri oga.
\v 32 Zvino vatariri vengoro vakati vachiona Jehoshafati, vakati, Zvirokwazvo ndiye mambo waIsraeri. Vakatsaukira kundorwa naye; zvino Jehoshafati akaridza mhere.
\v 33 Ipapo vatariri vengoro vakati vachiona kuti haazi mambo waIsraeri, vakadzoka pakumutevera.
\v 34 Zvino umwe  murume akabwembura uta hwake asingashumbi, hake, akafura mambo waIsraeri pakati pezvisungo zvenguvo dzake dzokurwa nadzo, ipapo mambo akati kumufambisi wengoro yake, Dzoka, undiise kunze kwehondo, nekuti ndakuvadzwa kwazvo.
\p
\v 35 Kurwa kukanyanya kwazvo nomusi uyo; mambo akatsigirwa mungoro yake pakurwa navaSiriya, akafa madekwani; ropa rikabuda pavanga rikaerera mukati mengoro.
\v 36 Zvino zuva rakati rovira mhere ikanzwika pahondo yose, ichiti, umwe  neumwe   ngaadzokere kuguta rake, umwe  neumwe   kunyika yake.
\p
\v 37 Naizvozvo mambo akafa, akaiswa Samaria, vakaviga mambo paSamaria.
\v 38 Vakasuka ngoro padziva reSamaria, imbwa dzikananzva ropa rake, ndipo paishamba zvifeve; sezvakange zvarehwa neshoko raJehovha.
\p
\v 39 Zvino mamwe mabasa aAhabhi, nezvose zvaakaita, neimba yenyanga dzenzou yaakavaka, namaguta ose aakavaka, hazvina kunyorwa here mubhuku yaMakoronike amadzimambo aIsraeri?
\p
\v 40 Naizvozvo Ahabhi akarara namadzibaba ake, Ahazia mwanakomana wake akamutevera paushe.
\p
\v 41 Zvino Jehoshafati mwanakomana waAsa, wakatanga kubata ushe hwaJudha negore rechina raAhabhi mambo waIsraeri.
\v 42 Jehoshafati wakange ava namakore makumi matatu namashanu pakutanga kwake kubata ushe; akabata makore makumi maviri namashanu paJerusarema. Zita ramai vake rakange riri Azubha, mukunda waShirihi.
\v 43 Akafamba panzira dzose dzababa vake Asa; haana kutsauka padziri, asi wakaita zvakarurama pamberi paJehovha; kunyange zvakadaro matunhu akakwirira haana kubviswa, vanhu vakaramba vachingobayira nokupisira zvinonhuhwira pamatunhu akakwirira.
\v 44 Jehoshafati akayanana namambo waIsraeri.
\p
\v 45 Zvino mamwe mabasa aJehoshafati, nesimba rakaonekwa kwaari, nokurwa kwake, hazvina kunyorwa here mubhuku yaMakoronike amadzimambo aJudha?
\v 46 VaSodhomiwo vakange vasiiwa pamazuva aAsa baba vake, akavabvisawo panyika.
\p
\v 47 Asi paEdhomu pakange pasina mambo umwe  wakange achibata panzvimbo yamambo.
\p
\v 48 Jehoshafati akavaka zvikepe zveTarishishi kuenda Ofiri kuzotora ndarama; asi hazvina kuenda, nekuti zvikepe zvakaputsika paEZiyonigebheri.
\v 49 Zvino Ahazia mwanakomana waAhabhi akati kuna Jehoshafati, Varanda vangu ngavaende navaranda vako nezvikepe. Asi Jehoshafati wakaramba.
\p
\v 50 Jehoshafati akarara namadzibaba ake, akavigwa kuna madzibaba ake paguta raDhavhidhi baba vake, Jehorami mwanakomana wake akamutevera paushe.
\p
\v 51 Ahazia mwanakomana waAhabhi, akatanga kubata ushe hwaIsraeri paSamaria pagore regumi namanomwe raJehoshafati mambo waJudha, akabata ushe hwaIsraeri makore maviri.
\v 52 Akaita zvakaipa pamberi paJehovha, akafamba nenzira yababa vake, uye nenzira yamai vake, uye nenzira yaJerobhoamu mwanakomana waNebhati, wakatadzisa Israeri.
\v 53 Nekuti wakashumira Bhaari, akanamata kwaari, akatsamwisa Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri, sezvakaita baba vake pazvose.
